Package view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalyzerFrame
    This class represents a frame in which the data collected during the run of the motor are analyzed with our implementation of Analyzer called TirocinioAnalyzer.
    CustomClassRenderer
    Class for displaying a JComboBox of Class using their method Class.getSimpleName() to get the string to display inside a JLabel
    CustomPortRenderer
    Class for displaying a JComboBox of CommPortIdentifier using their method CommPortIdentifier.getName() to get the string to display inside a JLabel
    GraphsFrame
    This class implements a simple JFrame which display the data extracted from the data file in a previous run in a series of ctarts as done in GraphTelemetryView.
    GraphTelemetryView
    This class represents a frame in which the data collected during the run of the motor are displayed in the most proper way.
    LeftPanel
    In LeftPanel are displayed all the options concerning routines and escs, using three combo box and a button.
    MainFrame
    MainFrame è la classe principale della GUI, nella quale vengono mostrati LeftPanel e RightPanel e quindi si ha la possibilità di selezionare l'esc e la porta e far partire la routine, o selezionare un file di dati ed eventualmente di properties per analizzarlo.
    RightPanel
    In RightPanel are displayed all the options concerning log file analysis, using two file chooser, a combo box and two button.
    SimpleTelemetryView
    The first prototype of a view able to display the changing values of a running telemetry.
